This library is a wrapper around the Pango library, available at:
	http://www.pango.org/

This library allows you to use TrueType fonts to render 
internationalized and tagged text in SDL applications.

See the file INSTALL for building and installation instructions.

See the file ./docs/html/index.html for usage.

See the file COPYING for copying conditions.

Please send all bug reports by e-mail to:
    nakamura@sbp.fp.a.u-tokyo.ac.jp
